Saturday thur Friday- I was at Belinda's house..hanging out with her and Lacey=fun

Friday Night- Belinda, Martina, Larry and I went bowling in canton..my high score was 80 lol Larry had the highest score which was 111 (shit house)..Lacey came home with us

Saturday- Woke up at 10:30..played hide and seek with Lacey..at 1:00 we went to the fire hall for lunch..came home made a few phone calls..went to canton took Lacey home..went and picked up Kristin..meant up with Darcie at wal-mart..then to the ground floor..Mockina (which was the second band that played) we have been talking to ahead of time..there from New Jersey..so we hung out with them..got in free..got free shirts..free drinks..and hung out in there awesome camper..it was a house on wheels..it had everything..a master bedroom, bathroom(even with a shower), a tv, and a fire place. It was fun..I was even on the stage..oh and they offered us a beach house to stay in (score) sometime in June..there playing again in May..everyone should go and watch them..after the concert we went out to eat at Wendy's..Kristin's cheese burger..didnt have cheese..(yeah) so we back thur the drive thur..they threw her sandwich away..and they gave for two..over all a fun night

And well today is Easter..HAPPY EASTER!! WOOHOO were having HAM! The Easter Bunny already came and now is gone..I missed him again 

Surprise..SURPRISE..:)

Big fight with my parents last night..so maybe writing it down will help..lets see friday night I wanted to go to the donkey basketball game butttttttttt no..I didnt even get a reason why I couldnt go..just wasnt allowed..I'm 19 and can't go to a basketball game..what the hell..okay and then Saturday morning I wake up and my parents are gone!! My little sister Rebecca was at a friends house and calls..comes home..but not just her she brings her little friend too..I had plans to hang out with Richele..but nooooooooo I was stuck babysitting all day..from 10am-till 11:30pm at night..I cleaned the whole kitchen with Martina..Didnt even get a thanks..so yeah I flipped out..I never swear (hardly) but you should have heard me..Every other word..I was pissed..After, a lonnnnnnnnnng fight..I went to bed..Woke up thinking okay today I'll go see Richele..I didnt want to hang out here..But, today was Lacey's birthday party (she'll be 5 on Tuesday..shes growing up so fast) my sister Cherry came down from New York and brought baby Will down..her hushand Matt couldnt come..he had to work..well after the fight with my mom and dad the night before the last thing I wanted to do was hang out with them and family..put on a "happy face"..I wasnt going to go ..the only reason I did go was because it was Lacey's birthday and wanted to see her..Cherry had some news for us....guess...okay..shes having a second baby..so William will have a little sister or brother..and I'll be an adult again..which is cool..ate some cake, played hide-and-seek with Will, played with my little ponies with Lacey..After, Cherry left..Belindas best friend came over..with her hushand and three kids..a 5 month baby..she was soooo cute..I got to hold her and feed her..I love babies..Came home and did some kick boxing 

yeah my weekend..at least Cherry didnt drag me to church...

Doing okay in boring sulco..not awhole lot has happened..

A story about a boy I know.....
 

I recall my first time with a condom, I was 16 or
so.  I went in to buy a package of condoms.  There was
a beautiful
woman behind the counter, and she could see that I was
new at it.  She
handed me the package and asked, if I knew how to wear
one.  I
honestly answered, "No."  So she unwrapped the
package, took one out
and slipped over her thumb.  She cautioned me to make
sure it was on tight and secure.  I apparently
still looked confused.  So she looked all around the
store.  It
was empty. She said," "Just a minute."  And walked to
the door, and
locked it.
Taking my hand, she led me into the back room,
unbuttoned her blouse and
removed it . She
unhooked her bra and laid it aside.  She asked, "Do
these excite you?"
Well, I was so dumb-struck that all I could do was nod
my head.  She
then said, it was time to slip the condum on.  As I
was slipping it
on, she dropped her skirt, removed her panties and
laid down on a
desk.  "Well ,
come on", she said, "We don't have much time."  So I
climbed on
her.  It was so wonderful, that unfortunately, I could
no longer hold
back and pow, I was done within a few minutes. She
looked at me with a
frown.  "Did you put that condom on?"   I said, "I
sure did."
And held up my thumb to show her
